      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
                                   
        Mike Catt's Blue team √Ļ comprising Mark Foster, Martin Offiah 
        and Jane Couch √Ļ competes against Kelly Holmes' Reds √Ļ Iwan 
        Thomas, Roberto Di Matteo and Graham Thorpe √Ļ for the right 
        to meet Steve Redgrave's Whites in the final next week. Over 
        six tense rounds, the two are evenly matched but one will come 
        out victorious

